ai.harmony.ravel.compiler.symbol

Class SymbolWithScope

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.harmony.ravel.compiler.scope.BaseScope
      • ai.harmony.ravel.compiler.symbol.SymbolWithScope
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Scope, Symbol
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ComponentSymbol, EventHandlerSymbol, MethodDeclarationSymbol

    public abstract class SymbolWithScope
extends BaseScope
implements Symbol, Scope
    An abstract base class that houses common functionality for symbols like classes and functions that are both symbols and scopes. There is some common cut and paste functionality with BaseSymbol because of a lack of multiple inheritance in Java but it is minimal.
